nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO EXPECTED TO STRENGTHEN DURING THE COMING DAYS...
summary: ...HUMBERTO EXPECTED TO STRENGTHEN DURING THE COMING DAYS... As of 11:00 PM AST Wed Sep 24 the center of Humberto was located near 20.7, -55.8 with movement WNW at 12 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
